Description_zh-Hant:
選擇一名指定對象，吞噬目標身上的所有負面異常，並
將異常儲存入奈奈的“胃囊”，獲得不超過10點的厄運魔
能，對目標造成{0}點傷害<br>冷卻：10回合。 剩餘冷卻:{1}

Description_en:
Select a target that devours all negative anomalies on the target, and
Store the anomaly in Nana's "stomach pouch" to obtain no more than 10 points of {buff_DoomPower} 
, dealing {0} damage to the target(if is not self).Remaining cooldown: {1}
